cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use marinaMoji, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: marinaMoji
abstract: >-
  Open-source Japanese input method (IME) for scholars of classical and
  premodern Japanese. Fork of Mozc with historical kana, kyūjitai/shinjitai
  conversion, odoriji and kaeriten marks, floating toolbar, and optional
  encrypted cross-device sync. macOS (Input Method Kit) and Linux (IBus).
authors:
