      CNRS
    orcid: https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9115-3931
  - family-names: Pandolfino
    given-names: Marina
    affiliation: >-
      Centre de recherche sur les civilisations de l'Asie orientale (CRCAO),
      École pratique des hautes études (EPHE)
repository-code: https://github.com/marinaMoji/marinaMoji
url: https://norbert.huma-num.fr/marinamoji
license: BSD-3-Clause
keywords:
  - Japanese input method
  - IME
  - Mozc
  - premodern Japanese
  - digital humanities
  - kanbun
